org.chronos.chronograph.internal.impl.structure.graph

Class ChronoGraphVariables

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.chronos.chronograph.internal.impl.structure.graph.ChronoGraphVariables
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Graph.Variables

    public class ChronoGraphVariables
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Graph.Variables
    Implementation of the Gremlin interface.

    This implementation persists the graph variables alongside the actual graph data, i.e. graph.tx().commit() will also commit the graph variables, and graph.tx().rollback() will remove any changes.
